dc_description_s: This ESRI Geodatabase contains polygon features and attribute data tables for census data for the country of Guatemala. The data is derived from the nstitutio Nacional de Estadistica and was released in 2010. The data contain 28,000 census boundary polygons that each have 127 attributes, and the lowest administrative boundary level represented is Barrios. Refer to the documentation for a list of variables and a translation of variable titles into English. For more information on the census methodology and a glossary of variable categories, go to the INE website at https://www.ine.gob.gt/.
